{"tid":1932854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(武漢肺炎)  意大利前通訊部長怒吊 : 「中国是地球毒瘤」","createTime":"2020-03-19T03:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T02:51:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":783,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"4c1219207884dd9c2b52ffe36c4d1da1d11c0aa5","tid":1932854,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/03/18/phpPPQ9Df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F03%2F18%2FphpPPQ9Df.jpg&h=b504fde7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖擷取自YouTube「台灣佛克斯 Taiwan Focus」）<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎侵襲世界各地，中國政府近日強化大外宣，企圖用官媒和外交系統營造「全球救世主」的形象，卻慘遭義大利媒體踢爆，中國聲稱的物資援助全都是「商業交易」；對此，義國參議員加斯帕里（Maurizio Gasparri）痛批「中國是地球的毒瘤」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，中國近日藉由大量出口醫療物資，在國際上增強「抗疫有成」、「中國模式」等政治宣傳，被多家義媒看破手腳，狠批「中義友好」全是「慈善假新聞」，曾任通信部長的義國參議員加斯帕里，17日也拍片狠嗆中國。<br />\n<br />\n加斯帕里表示：「中國從來沒有無償送義大利任何東西，所有物資都是我們自己花錢買的，中國是地球上最糟糕的一個國家，經常以不正當的競爭手段，讓其他國家陷入經濟危機。」<br />\n<br />\n加斯帕里怒嗆，中國是一個塑膠汙染與碳排放最嚴重的國家，對這次的武漢病毒隱瞞疫情，在共產黨專制領導下，甚至故意拖延時間以及提供假訊息，「中國是地球的毒瘤」。<br />\n<br />\n最後，加斯帕里呼籲，義大利要下定決心勇敢面對中國，用有限的經濟手段反制，「歐洲需要從這樣的狀況中醒悟，不要再被中國的謊言欺騙了，中國對於地球來說並不是一個資源，而是一個危險」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3104383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3104383&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzEngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=f1af3799\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3104383&h=ae3af863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3104383</a>"},{"pid":"eefd32f30f6203c8ac496f45a4c235e1353676f1","tid":1932854,"uid":62714,"like":209,"dislike":2,"score":207,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:20:11.000Z","msg":"宜家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩一戴一露玩到你咁爽呀啦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18452fd11e5fec94e1275f47b01511f08deb19ae","tid":1932854,"uid":301989,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"依家先知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae6505795fe42e582c82f92aa6d6b25a13476b0","tid":1932854,"uid":103063,"like":78,"dislike":2,"score":76,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:42:07.000Z","msg":"亲 現在才知道<br />\n一切都太晚了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奶呀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368b531a0a1bf8dfc562a2f0967714c33a444487","tid":1932854,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:54:17.000Z","msg":"奶晒野"},{"pid":"15ce1732fe7ea82123e212558132c9ce460a7f6f","tid":1932854,"uid":269680,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"依加先知 唔殺撚到埋身唔會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1557b2fdada0b591c16c2dcd6498c0e468e8ec","tid":1932854,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:55:19.000Z","msg":"well said"},{"pid":"0bbf537b5a832dfc059a12665a7b344e5998b29e","tid":1932854,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:55:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n[我日日都食雞！]武漢話冇事啦，中南海係咪先帶頭搬去一年半載工作？？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/19/114839_68e4bdb58d864a370089c0b88549439e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F19%2F114839_68e4bdb58d864a370089c0b88549439e.png&h=cbf68cf